    "is_snapshot": true,
    "description": "Estimated FBA fee preview snapshots. Amazon ships one row per (sku, marketplace); multi-marketplace stores produce N×M rows. MENA TSVs (AE/SA) omit product-size-weight-band, has-local-inventory, and all EU EFN fee columns.",
